---
title: Foundations
meta: Eight essential systems that sustain households and communities
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}
{% block content %}
<section id="foundations">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2.2rem; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0; color: var(--accent); text-align: center;">Foundations</h1>
  <p class="section-description" style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem; color: var(--muted);">
    Waterbear Field School organizes learning around eight foundations - the essential systems that sustain households and communities. Each foundation contains workshops ranging from accessible introductions to advanced builds. Take them individually, or join a <a href="/resilience-sequence/">Resilience Sequence</a> to work through multiple foundations with a cohort.
  </p>
  <div class="grid foundations-grid">
    {% for p in collections.allFoundations %}
    <article class="card foundation-card" data-foundation="{{ p.data.foundation }}">
      <a href="{{ p.url }}" class="thumb" aria-label="{{ p.data.title }}">
        {% if p.data.image %}
          <img src="{{ p.data.image }}" alt="{{ p.data.title }}" />
        {% else %}
          <div class="foundation-placeholder foundation-{{ p.data.foundation }}">{{ p.data.title | slice(0, 1) }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </a>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3><a href="{{ p.url }}">{{ p.data.title }}</a></h3>
        {% if p.data.meta %}<div class="meta-description">{{ p.data.meta }}</div>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--card); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--hair);">
    <h2 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ready to dive deeper?</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Resilience Sequence is a 4-week cohort program covering energy, climate, communication, and making.</p>
    <a href="/resilience-sequence/" class="button" style="display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none;">Learn about the Sequence</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
